<HEADLINE>
<P>
BROCCOLI 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
You may be disinterested to know that gardening is my hobby and that I have 
hybridized a new strain of broccoli. 
</P>
<P>
It will not be grown as an annual but rather as a shrub. 
</P>
<P>
In honor of our President I have named it the Broccoli Bush. Wish me luck. 
</P>
<P>
Yes, I may use pork rinds for fertilizer. 
</P>
<P>
PARKE LEVY 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
