<P>
KCRW to Link U.S.-Israel: Public-radio station KCRW-FM (89.9) at noon today 
will broadcast "This Year in Israel," a two-hour, live show that it claims is 
the first national call-in program linking an American audience with Israel. 
Ruth Hirschman, KCRW general manager, will host the program, timed to coincide 
with Passover, from a live feed in Jerusalem. SHAUNA SNOW 
