SCIENTISTS; LUMBER INDUSTRY -- NORTHERN CALIFORNIA; LUMBER INDUSTRY -- 
WASHINGTON (STATE); LUMBER INDUSTRY -- OREGON; FISH AND WILDLIFE SERVICE 
(U.S.); ENVIRONMENTALISTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
