LIFE; DEPORTATION; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; MAURITANIA -- BORDERS -- SENEGAL; 
SENEGAL -- CULTURE; GAMBIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SENEGAL; GUINEA BISSAU -- 
