Tampa Avenue and Rinaldi Street in Chatsworth. DAVID BOHRER / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, The Rev. Jess Moody conducts services in Shepherd of the Hills' 
temporary quarters at Mason Park Recreation Center in Chatsworth. DAVID BOHRER 
/ Los Angeles Times; Photo, The Rev. Jess Moody, Pastor of Shepherd of the 
Hills Church 
