<TEXT>
<P>
Willamette Industries Inc. said it acquired Penntech Papers Inc. of White 
Plains, N.Y. for an undisclosed sum. 
</P>
<P>
Penntech, which produces specialty grades of fine paper, will be operated as a 
separate subsidiary of Willamette, said Willamette President and Chief 
